description:
Eddie Gomez Interview by Tonatiuh Vázquez

Talks about his first steps in music, his experiences with the jazz icons such as Bill Evans, Benny Godman and Chick Corea among others. He also talks about his labor as a jazz educator at the CMPR and how his music has been changing through the years.

Entrevista con Eddie Gomez por Tonatiuh Vázquez

Habla acerca de sus primeros pasos por la música, sus experiencias con los iconos de jazz como Bill Evans, Benny Godman y Chick Corea entre otros. También habla de su labor como educador de jazz en el CMPR y como su música ha estado cambiando a travez de los años.
title: Eddie Gomez Interview
